# This file exists to keep the empty folder under version control.
#
# Drop client-provided Screener-style exports here, named <companyId>.xlsx
# (or .csv). The parser `npm run ingest:screener` will pick them up.
#
# Examples (when supplied):
#   tcs.xlsx
#   infosys.xlsx
#   hcltech.xlsx
#   wipro.xlsx
#
# These files are import-backed, NOT source-backed. They never merge
# into the official financial snapshots.
